                                <p class="fs-5 fw-medium text-dark">
                                    <i class="bi bi-quote text-success fs-1 me-2 align-top"></i>
                                    It is with great pleasure and a deep sense of responsibility that I take this opportunity to reach out to our current and potential clientele.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <p class="fs-5">
                                    Greenlane College welcomed its first students in 2010. Since then, we have welcomed a growing list of thousands of students, many of whom have graduated from some of the best South African universities. I would like to reiterate our professional and qualified staff's commitment to establish a socially friendly and academically positive learning environment to enable our learners to fulfill their utmost potential.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <div class="row g-4 mb-4">
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <div class="card h-100 border-start border-primary border-3">
                                            <div class="card-body p-3">
                                                <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                                                    <i class="bi bi-people-fill text-success fs-3 me-3"></i>
                                                    <div>
                                                        <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2">To Our Parents</h5>
                                                        <p class="text-muted small">Your partnership and support are immeasurable.</p>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <div class="card h-100 border-start border-success border-3">
                                            <div class="card-body p-3">
                                                <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                                                    <i class="bi bi-mortarboard-fill text-success fs-3 me-3"></i>
                                                    <div>
                                                        <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2">To Our Students</h5>
                                                        <p class="text-muted small">Fulfill your utmost potential in our nurturing environment.</p>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <p class="fs-5">
                                    To our previous and current parents, thank you for trusting Greenlane College staff to educate and guide your children. We trust that your children benefit from our vibrant and inclusive community by growing their body of knowledge, skills, and values. Your partnership and support are immeasurable. Together, we have formed a team that guides and shapes our children's future.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-success">Our Strategic Location</h4>
                                <div class="location-card p-4 bg-light rounded mb-3">
                                    <div class="row g-3 align-items-center">
                                        <div class="col-md-2 text-center">
                                            <i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill text-success fs-1"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-10">
                                            <p class="fs-5 mb-0">
                                                Greenlane College is located in vibrant Johannesburg, accessible to major taxi, bus, and train routes. The location was chosen for its quiet and peaceful environment away from the hustle and bustle of the city center.
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <p class="fs-5">
                                    I invite you to visit our website for more detailed information about us, our curriculum, extramural activities, and to easily apply to join Greenlane College.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="closing-message p-4 bg-success bg-opacity-10 rounded border-start border-success border-4">
                                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-success">Our Commitment to Excellence</h4>
                                <p class="fs-5 mb-0">
                                    I conclude by reiterating our resolve to provide a safe and nurturing environment, ensuring high-quality education and training, and fostering a holistic approach to developing our learners. We shall keep abreast of the latest initiatives and developments in the ever-changing educational landscape.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Signature -->
                        <div class="signature-section mt-5 pt-4 border-top">
                            <div class="row align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-md-8">
                                    <div class="mb-2">
                                        <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-dark">Jamil Lubega</div>
                                        <div class="text-muted">Principal & Academic Director</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text-muted">
                                        <i class="bi bi-calendar me-2"></i> January 2026
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4 text-md-end">
                                    <div class="signature-image">
                                        <img src="/images/principal/signature.png" alt="Principal's Signature" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 200px; opacity: 0.9;">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
